==English==
===Etymology===
From the uniform of [[white]] [[shirt]] and [[shorts]] worn by the Victorian Football League (which became the [[w:Australian Football League|Australian Football League]]) field umpires.  The umpires' uniforms changed to day-glow orange in 2004.
